    <briefdescription>
<para>nPM6001-specific GPIO Flags </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The drive flags are encoded in the 8 upper bits of <ref refid="group__gpio__interface_1gad435719dccdc37c05852960a7218fbd2" kindref="member">gpio_dt_flags_t</ref> as follows:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Bit 8: Drive strength (0=NORMAL, 1=HIGH)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit 9: Input type (0=SCHMITT, 1=CMOS) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
